node.text:
Is your dream suit so unique that only really you could design it? If so, we have a surprise for you! Introducing our D.I.Y. Swimsuit Kit. It comes with everything you need to sew your perfect suit from scratch. Sound crazy? It's easier than you'd think! Link in bio to find out more! 

#jolyn #diy #swimsuit

node.text:
Brianna Boney @gnarlygirlfitness⁠
Vegas LEGEND on the trails and at the crags. 🤙⁠
⁠
Bri is a behavioral change expert/ outdoors woman. ⁠
She is a pillar of the female mountain biking and rock climbing communities in the Vegas area. ⁠
⁠
Bri is public about having suffered through an eating disorder for 10 years and utilizes her experiences with negative self talk and being overly restrictive when working with her clients. ⁠
Ps Bri is an incredible land athlete taking the leap and getting into the pool!!! 🏊‍♀️⁠
⁠
Bri organizes “GNARLY GIRL” rides and climbing meetups in addition to her nutrition and athletics coaching. ⁠
⁠
Bri’s philosophy is centered around mindfulness and intentional progress. Nothing is “bad” everything in moderation. Bri educates her clients on how to properly fuel themselves to just live the lives they aspire to. ⁠
⁠
